@using CRMVIETTOUR.Utilities
@using CRMVIETTOUR.Models
@using CRM.Core
@model tbl_TaskHandling
<div class="modal fade  bs-modal-lg" id="modal-work-task" role="document" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
        @using (Html.BeginForm("WorkTask", "TaskManage"))
        {
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true"></button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title">Xử lý nhiệm vụ</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="form-horizontal">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label class="control-label col-lg-3 col-md-3">Tình trạng</label>
                                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3">
                                        <select class="form-control" style="width: 100%" name="StatusId" id="work-task-status">
                                            @foreach (var item in LoadData.TaskStatusList())
                                            {
                                                <option value="@item.Id">@item.Name</option>
                                            }
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                    <label class="control-label col-lg-3 col-md-3">% hoàn thành</label>
                                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3">
                                        @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.PercentFinish, new { @class = "form-control", @type = "number", min = 0, max = 100,  })
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label class="control-label col-lg-3 col-md-3">Ghi chú hoặc lý do</label>
                                    <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-9">
                                        @Html.TextAreaFor(model => model.Note, new { @class = "form-control", id = "work-note" })
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label class="control-label col-lg-3 col-md-3">File đính kèm</label>
                                    <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-9">
                                        @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.File, new { type = "file", @class = "form-control", id = "WorkTaskFile" })
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div align="center" style="margin-bottom: 20px">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn blue" id="btnLuuThem">Thực hiện</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn default" data-dismiss="modal">Đóng</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        <!-- /.modal-content -->
        }
    </div>
    <!-- /.modal-dialog -->
</div>
